title: TreeViewSearch Props
description:
Renders a search input for the tree view. This sub-component should be passed into the
tree view component's toolbar property.

aria-label.description: Accessible label for the search input.

className.description: Classes applied to the wrapper for the search input.

onSearch.description: Callback for search input. (Function: (event: React.ChangeEvent<HTMLInputElement>) => void)
